  <entry>
    <title>为文字版ubuntu配置中文支持</title>
    <link href="http://suilin.top/2019/10/12/%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E7%89%88ubuntu%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/"/>
    <id>http://suilin.top/2019/10/12/为文字版ubuntu配置中文支持/</id>
    <published>2019-10-12T14:43:02.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-12T14:45:37.134Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>安装中文包:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install language-pack-zh*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置环境变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//首先</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/environment</span><br><span class="line">//在上面的文件中加入下面的设置</span><br><span class="line">LANG=<span class="string">"zh_CN.UTF-8"</span></span><br><span class="line">LANGUAGE=<span class="string">"zh_CN:zh:en_US:en"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重新设置环境变量选项</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg-reconfigure locales</span><br><span class="line">// 然后选择全部区域中使用 zh_CN.UTF-8 即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
